-jannah-thorny-tree\/","url_meta":{"origin":32279,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Thorns: Man enjoys Paradise for clearing out a thorny tree","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 18, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: There was a tree in the road that used to harm people, so a man came and cleared it from the road. The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cI have seen him enjoying himself in its shade in Paradise.\u201d Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 12332\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":35053,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/01\/25\/good-dunya-akhirah\/","url_meta":{"origin":32279,"position":5},"title":"Hasan on Dua: Goodness is knowledge in world, Paradise in Hereafter","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 25, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Hisham ibn Hassan reported: Al-Hasan, may Allah have mercy on him, said in regards to His saying, \u201cO Lord, give us good in the world and good in the Hereafter,\u201d (2:201) that good in the world is knowledge and worship, and good in the Hereafter is Paradise. Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/32279","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/post